1. Upload Advanced Woo Search Plugin: https://tl.wordpress.org/plugins/advanced-woo-search/
2. Activate Plugin then click 'Reindex Table'.
3. Copy the shortcode.
4. Go to header then look for the form of search bar.
Static Form:
<form class="form" action="#" method="post">
   <input class="head_input" type="text" name="Search" placeholder="search" required />
   <input type="submit" name="submit_info" value="Submit" />
</form>

Dynamic Form
<div class="form">
   <?php echo do_shortcode('[aws_search_form]'); ?>
</div>

Note: e copy ra nimo kung unsa ang class sa form.

5. Then inspect and copy kung unsa ang style sa class sa input static, then e change ang kani na class sa common.css sa file:
.aws-container .aws-search-field {

}
Note: Use Path:
https://w3735.proweaversite3.com/wp-content/plugins/advanced-woo-search/assets/css/common.css?ver=2.53

6. Done.
